title: Upload Files on Aws S3 Bucket
tags: @zettel aws _method
roam-id: e94f4f41-1fe3-4ac7-b27e-e6fe3a1700cd
type: text/markdown

assume we have an s3 bucket named `s3-92827`

- upload a single file

``` shell
aws s3 cp ./file.txt s3://s3-92827/
```

- upload a directory )

``` shell
aws s3 cp ./folder s3://s3-92827/ --recursive
```
